   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00043-B-00002-000-00303"/>Herrn Dr Arthur
                  Schnitzler</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb50">Wien</rs></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb168940" type="place">XVIII Spöttelgasse 7</rs></hi></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><p><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00043-B-00002-000-00304"/><salute>Lieber,</salute><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><rs ref="#pmb3130" type="person">Clemens Francken<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tein</rs> bittet mich,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>einen Dank
               zu <subst><del rend="overwritten">Ü</del><add place="inline">ü</add></subst>bermitteln für gütige Zu<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>endung Ihres <rs type="work" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb29923">Buches</rs>, da er Ihre Adre<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>e nicht weiß.</p><p>Ich hoffe, baldig<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t von Ihnen zu hören, da<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>s Sie in der Arbeit u. zufrieden<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ind. Ich
               arbeite.</p><closer>Von Herzen.<lb/><signed>Hugo.</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
